data.description: Discover the allure of Las Vegas living at 10180 Pensive Ponder St in the tranquil, gated, Mountains Edge community of Aspire. This residence features upgraded cabinetry, immense natural light, a spacious open floor plan, a chefs kitchen with large walk-in pantry, oversized island and tons of counter space. This residence offers tasteful finishes throughout, a built in outdoor kitchen that includes a six burner gas grill, refrigerator and marble counter tops. This home features 3 bedrooms in total, plus a bonus room/office/den. The primary suite is expansive with vaulted ceilings, dual vanities in the en-suite bathroom and oversized walk-in closet. Situated on a large oversized lot, this 2,973 square foot property is complete with a 3 car garage that adds to the luxury and convenience of this Mountain’s Edge property. Motivated seller entertaining all reasonable offers
